Charles Belcher (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Belcher_(actor) 0 Charles Belcher (27 July 1872 – 10 December 1943) was an American film actor. He appeared in 17 films between years 1919 and 1928. He was born in San Francisco and died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles.
